---
title: Thai Green Fish Curry with Jasmine Rice & Lemon
description: We’re heating things up by using Thai green curry paste in this creamy sauce, adding a depth and spice that’ll cure any case of tired tastebuds. Balance it out with a bed of jasmine rice and a burst of lemony citrus to complete this perfect plate.
